<br>
<br>
It's illegal to shoot of fire works in Denver, but not illegal to sell any.<br>
<br>
<br>
on the 4th of july, DPD grossed like $250,000 off of fire works tickets. It just shows you how fucked up the city is. I bet you the government was even selling the fireworks.<br>
