&quot;Marajuana is like 200 times more dangerous than cigaretts.&quot;<br>
<br>
yeah....but how many cigaretts does a person smoke each day? <br>
<br>
I've seen people go through packs in a single day. and the average weed smoker will smoke 1 joint a day...many times sharing with another person, or a group of people.<br>
<br>
<br>
Weed being addictive....<br>
<br>
<br>
Now, here's something I agree on. I think weed is very addictive....about as addictive as cigarettes. My brother once walked a mile in like 2ft snow just to get some....the roads were closed, and everyone was off from school...him and his friend wanted some, and they tried for 2 hours to find someone who had some...then spent another 2 hours walking to get it, and walking back.<br>
<br>
Weed messing with metality.<br>
<br>
<br>
I agree here....Weed is bad for the the personality....A person who smokes weed will be fine, when they aren't smoking weed, nothing really seems to matter to them. They have mood swings, and if things aren't going well, they get pissed off easier than they would if they werent on weed.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
My overall view of weed.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
1) weed is good for social situations much like alcohol is....It can make tense situations more relaxing....alot of this is due to people passing the blunt/pipe =)....*its easier to say you wanna take a hit, rather than hi...my name is* Plus, you don't look stupid if they reject your offer ;)*<br>
<br>
2) smoking weed should be used on an occasional basis, and not for every day life.<br>
<br>
3) weed makes funny movies VERY FUNNY.<br>
<br>
4) doing weed all the time can fuck up your life.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
I'm no expert on weed, but I have been in contact with it for probably a good 3rd of my life. It isn't by any means this wonderful thing that should be done during church. But it's not as bad as TV comercials, and school programs make it up to be.<br>
<br>
Weed is the gateway drug....this is true, it can lead into different things if someone isn't careful, and knowleged about it....that's why it should have an age restriction.<br>
<br>
My brother started doing weed his Sophmore year...He then tried shrooms...which i guess he never really liked, because I never saw him do it....unlike weed, which I saw him do all the time. He told me he even did Acid once.....which freaked me out, cause that's one of the &quot;bad&quot; drugs. But he said he did it once, and never wanted to try it again.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
